name: Crystal Flora HEN600K
description: @__lindaloh__ 3D diamond sculpture, with abstracted Australian kangaroo paw flowers, for the festive season and #hen600k. It is an adaptation of the crystal/diamond pieces in my genesis mints on HEN, around #hen500k, which were part of a collection of 20 individual sculptural pieces from my VR world "Agog", 2021. They are variously luminous, poetic, evocative, shiny, scribbly, wacky, simple, sleek, golden, wonky, compelling, weird, colourful, minimal, maximal, simple, ethereal…
